data.description: Don't miss this 3 bed 2 bath home on 4.78 open acreage. This home was updated in 2022 with new kitchen cabinets, countertops, stainless steel appliances, flooring, New HVAC, 40 Gal water heater, and more. The back 3 acres of land are fenced in and ready for cattle.  The property is right off Hwy 13 just south of Warrensburg about 10 a minute's drive to Warrensburg and 15 minutes from Whiteman AFB. This property won't last long so book your showing Today!
